<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-4218] Set TCP_NODELAY for PHP client socket</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-4218</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The PHP client doesn&apos;t set the TCP_NODELAY socket option like C++, C#, Ruby, or Java.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This patch enables TCP_NODELAY for the client socket.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
